    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-01-03T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-01-03T14:00:00-05:00" n="598"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d598">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 European War 1939/26938: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Aden (<persName type="from"
                            >Timberlake</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Aden</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-01-03T22:00:00+03:00"
                            >January 3, 1943—10 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received January 5—6:59 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1. French Somaliland capitulated on December 28 without a shot having been fired.
                        Agreement<note n="58" xml:id="d598fn58">The agreement was dated December 28,
                        1942.</note> signed by General Dupont, Fowkes and Chancel places colony
                    under Free French with British liaison in all essential services such as port,
                    railway, radio and security. <pb facs="0617" n="611" xml:id="pg_611"/>
                    Bayardelle is our new Governor, P. Antoine, Pouvreau, Monnot, Delge and 5 others
                    made prisoners of war.</p>
                <p>Fifteen Italian Armistice Commissioners also prisoners. I asked Hopkinson to
                    suggest and recommend turning Commissioners over to us for trading purposes. He
                    agreed and said he did not believe British wanted them. Suggest Department
                    approach London this respect.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Timberlake</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
